	<div class="sp_head">
		<div class="sp_title">
			<h3 class="title bold t1 s1 i_b_t1"><mark class="cm">국민영양</mark> 학술지 미수령</h3>
		</div>
		<div class="sp_navi">
			<ul>
				<li class="start"><a href="index.jsp" class="icon_home"><span class="ti">HOME</span></a></li>
				<li><a href="/mypage/kmp_member_info.do">마이페이지</a></li>
				<li><a href="/mypage/kmp_magazine" class="cm">국민영양/학술지 미수령</a></li>
